quran[6]{c,v,t,f}:
  5,115,"Allah jwatite: “Chisimu Une tinajitulusye kukwenu, nambo jwachakane panyuma pakwe mwa jenumanja, basitu Une chinallagasye ni ilagasyo ya nganinallagasyeje nayo jwalijose mu iwumbe yosope.”"
  5,116,"Soni (kumbuchilani) katema katachiŵecheta Allah (lisiku lya Kiyama pa kum’buusya Isa) kuti: “E mmwe Isa mwanache jwa Maryam! Ana mmwe mwasalile ŵandu yanti: ‘Mundendani une ni mama ŵangu kuŵa milungu jiŵili mmalo mwa Allah?” Jwalakwe tachiti: “Kuswejela ni Kwenu! Nganiyiŵa yakundisidwa kukwangu kuti mbechete yanganiyiŵajilwa kukwangu, ingaŵe naiche mwakuŵecheta yalakweyo, basi chisimu nkayimanyi. Nkumanyilila yaili mu ntima mwangu, nambo une ngangumanyilila yaili mu ntima Mwenu, chisimu Mmwejo ni Ŵakumanyilila nnope yakusisika.”"
  5,117,"“Nganimbecheta kukwao ikaŵeje yamwanamwile yanti: ‘Mun'galagatileje Allah, M’mbuje gwangu soni M'mbuje gwenu.’ Soni naliji mboni pa ŵanganyao pa ndema janalonjele chilikati chao. Nambo katema kamwanjigele, Mmwejo ni ŵamwaliji ŵakwalolela ŵanganyao, soni Mmwe pa chindu chilichose m'bele Mboni.”"
  6,76,"Pandema jakwanswelele jwajiweni ndondwa, ni jwatite (melemelepe kusaka kwimusya lunda lwa makafili): “Aji (ndondwaji) ni m'mbuje gwangu.” Nambo ndema jajatiŵile jwatite: “Jwanganonyelwa (milungu) jakutiŵilaga.”"
  6,77,"Pandema jajwauweni mwesi uchikopokaga jwatite: “Aju ni m'mbuje gwangu.” Nambo ndema jawatiŵile jwatite: “Naga ngaakunjongola Ambuje ŵangu, chisimu timbe mu ŵandu ŵakupotela.”"
  6,78,"Pandema jajwaliweni lyuŵa lichikopokaga jwatite: “Aju ni m'mbuje gwangu, aju ni jwankulungwa kwannope.” Nambo ndema jalyakapile jwatite: “E ŵandu wangu! Chisimu une ndalikangene ni yankum'bwanganya nayo (Allah).”"